install nodemon and concurrently as dev dependecies in the root folder
npm i -D nodemon concurrently

nodemon is used so that we dont have to reset the server every time when we make changes in code 
"server": "nodemon backend/server"

add client script

and then add dev script with concurrently 


install dotenv 
create new file .env and we can incluse all our environment variables in that file for example port , db credentials etc


